OL,3,CUK Athletics partners with private
OL,4,Csector to help tackle financial crisis
OL,6,FCash-strapped has turned to the
OL,7,Forganisers of The London Marathon and
OL,8,Fthe Great North Run to help them
OL,9,Fnavigate their way out of a financial
OL,10,Fcrisis.
OL,12,FLast year the governing body reported
OL,13,Fan annual loss of #3.7m; the year
OL,14,Fbefore that the figure was almost #2m.
OL,15,FIn a word, their finances were
OL,16,Funsustainable.
OL,18,FCalled Athletic Ventures, the new
OL,19,Fthree-way partnership will attempt to
OL,20,Ftransform the "future and growth" of
OL,21,Fathletics in the UK.
