OL,3,CUK Athletics partners with private
OL,4,Csector to help tackle financial crisis
OL,6,FChief Executive Jack Buckner, told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "I do think it's important that
OL,8,Fin some areas you bring in the experts
OL,9,Fand specialists.
OL,11,F"Governing bodies have failed to
OL,12,Fdevelop the commercial end of the
OL,13,Fsport, and this is just a massive
OL,14,Fopportunity to do that."
OL,16,F"You end up having a relatively
OL,17,Fconstrained organisation, trying to do
OL,18,Fthese big bold exciting projects with
OL,19,Fa relatively high level of risk, that
OL,20,Fgets difficult."
