OL,3,CUK Athletics partners with private
OL,4,Csector to help tackle financial crisis
OL,6,FThe new group will run the 2026
OL,7,FEuropean Championships in Birmingham
OL,8,Fand the annual Diamond League meeting
OL,9,Fin the UK.
OL,11,FIt might also bid to host the World
OL,12,FChampionships in 2029.
OL,14,FKey to future financial success is
OL,15,Ffinding sponsors and securing major
OL,16,Fbroadcast partners so the sport and
OL,17,Fits athletes get a bigger profile -
OL,18,Frather than just once every 4 years at
OL,19,Fthe Olympic Games.
