OL,6,FPaul Foster, CEO of the Great Run
OL,7,FCompany which organises The Great
OL,8,FNorth Run, said: "The partnership is
OL,9,Fdriven not only by a belief in the
OL,10,Fsport of athletics but also the belief
OL,11,Fthat there is real commercial
OL,12,Fopportunity.
OL,14,F"We're bringing together the best
OL,15,Fevent organisers in our sport to
OL,16,Fcreate a new template for
OL,17,Finternational events."
